      <h1 class="wp-post-title">How To Make The Best, Simple Lasagna</h1>
      <p class="wp-post-deck">A Recipe for Lasagna with 4 Simple Ingredients and 8 Easy Steps</p>
    </header>

    <img
      class="wp-featured-img"
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574894709920-11b28e7367e3?w=860&h=380&fit=crop"
      alt="Lasagna"
